Most basic and general options all over the site are added inside the general options tab. In here you're able to change the logo, favicon, footer text and copyright, analytics, call to action and many more.

<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1904" title="general" src="http://wptitans.com/majestics/files/2011/08/general.png" alt="" width="570" height="1487" />

&nbsp;

Inside the homepage options tab your able to populate the homepage columns and activate or change the homepage slider. Plain and simple and full control of what going on.

<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1902" title="homepage" src="http://wptitans.com/majestics/files/2011/08/homepage.png" alt="" width="570" height="1594" />

&nbsp;

Inside the typography option tab your able to change fonts, cs of the body font and heading. You can select between Cufon and Google Web font and your able to use any font you like.

<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1895" title="typo" src="http://wptitans.com/majestics/files/2011/08/typo.png" alt="" width="570" height="1177" />

&nbsp;

Inside the media options tab your able to set the excerpt length of the portfolio items, the amount of items shown in the portfolios, the gallery options and flickr api settings.

<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1893" title="media" src="http://wptitans.com/majestics/files/2011/08/media.png" alt="" width="570" height="1530" />

&nbsp;
